description:
Greece: No Place to Die

Sociopolitical Documentary hosted by Chloe Hadjimatheou, published by BBC broadcasted as part of BBC Our World series in 2015 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/9/92/Greece-No-Place-to-Die-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
Chloe Hadjimatheou reports how Greece's biggest cities have run out of places to bury the dead. Graves are now rented rather than owned, and, after three years, bodies are exhumed to make space for new ones.
